<HEADLINE> Celebrity Birthdays  </HEADLINE>
By The Associated Press	   
<TEXT>
<P>
   Celebrity birthdays for the week of Sept. 24-30
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 24: Actor Gordon Clapp (''NYPD Blue'') is 52. Actor Kevin
Sorbo is 42. Singer Cedric Dent of Take 6 is 38.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 25: Actor Michael Douglas is 56. Actress Mimi Kennedy
(''Dharma and Greg'') is 51. Actor Anson Williams (''Happy Days'')
is 51. Actor Christopher Reeve is 48. Actress Heather Locklear is
39. Actor-rapper Will Smith is 32. Actress Catherine Zeta-Jones is
31.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 26: Singer Bryan Ferry is 55. Actress Mary Beth Hurt is
52. Singer Olivia Newton-John is 52. Singer-musician Cesar Rosas of
Los Lobos is 46. Actress Linda Hamilton is 44. Singer Tracy Thorn
of Everything But the Girl is 38. Singer Cindy Herron of En Vogue
is 35. Singer Shawn Stockman of Boyz II Men is 28.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 27: Actress Sada Thompson is 71. Actor Wilford Brimley is
66. Singer-musician Randy Bachman of Bachman-Turner Overdrive is
57. Actress Liz Torres is 53. Singer Meat Loaf is 49. Singer Mark
Calderon of Color Me Badd is 30. Actress Gwyneth Paltrow is 28.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 28: Actress Brigitte Bardot is 66. Writer-director-actor
John Sayles is 50. Actress-comedian Janeane Garofalo is 36. TV
personality Moon Zappa is 33.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 29: Singer Jerry Lee Lewis is 65. Musician Mike Pinera of
Iron Butterfly is 52. Singer-musician Mark Farner of Grand Funk
Railroad is 52. Actor-comedian Andrew ''Dice'' Clay is 42. Actress
Emily Lloyd is 30.
</P>
<P>
   Sept. 30: Singer Johnny Mathis is 65. Singer Marilyn McCoo is
57. Musician John Lombardo of 10,000 Maniacs is 48. Singer Deborah
Allen is 47. Actress Fran Drescher is 43. Actor Eric Stoltz is 39.
Rapper-producer Marley Marl is 38. Musician Robby Takac of the Goo
Goo Dolls is 36. Actress Jenna Elfman is 29. Actor Ashley Hamilton
is 26. Actress Lacey Chabert (''Party of Five'') is 18.
</P>
